                "desc": "<p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 215, 128)\">元素战技</span></p><p>造成2点<span style=\"color: #FF9999\">火元素伤害</span>，生成<span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">烈烧佑命护盾</span>。</p>",
