                "title": "真红炽火之大铠"
              },
              {
                "attributes": [],
                "desc": "<p><span>附着火元素，可发生元素反应：</span></p><p><span>【</span><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 153, 153)\">火元素</span><span>+</span><span style=\"color: rgb(153, 255, 255)\">冰元素</span><span>】</span><span style=\"color: white\">融化</span>：本伤害<span>+2</span></p><p><span>【</span><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 153, 153)\">火元素</span><span>+</span><span style=\"color: rgb(128, 192, 255)\">水元素</span><span>】</span><span style=\"color: white\">蒸发</span>：本伤害<span>+2</span></p><p><span>【</span><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 153, 153)\">火元素</span><span>+</span><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 172, 255)\">雷元素</span><span>】</span><span style=\"color: white\">超载</span>：本伤害<span>+2，目标强制切换到下一个角色</span></p><p><span>【</span><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 153, 153)\">火元素</span><span>+</span><span style=\"color: rgb(153, 255, 136)\">草元素</span><span>】</span><span style=\"color: white\">燃烧</span>：本伤害<span>+1，生成回合结束时造成1点火伤害的[</span><span style=\"color: white\">燃烧烈焰</span><span>]（可用次数1，最多叠加到2）</span></p>",
                "icon_url": "https://act-upload.hoyoverse.com/event-ugc-hoyowiki/2024/03/17/157749474/d714b3b669cc08d1d8e34464fd7a3630_4356514482911017845.png",
                "id": "talent22117",
                "key": "火元素伤害",
                "materials": [],
                "points": [
                  {
                    "point_count": 0,
                    "point_type": ""
                  }
                ],
                "talent_img": "",
                "title": "火元素伤害"
              },
              {
                "attributes": [],
                "desc": "<p><strong><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">物理伤害</span></strong></p><p>物理伤害不会附着元素，也不会发生元素反应。</p><p></p><p><strong><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">护盾</span></strong></p><p>此护盾所保护的角色受到伤害时，将会消耗护盾来抵消伤害。</p><p></p><p><strong><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">可用次数</span></strong></p><p>此牌效果触发后，会消耗1次<span style=\"color: white\">可用次数</span>；</p><p><span style=\"color: white\">可用次数</span>耗尽后，立刻弃置此牌。</p><p></p><p><strong><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">烈烧佑命护盾<br></span></strong><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 215, 128)\">出战状态</span></p><p>为我方出战角色提供1点<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">护盾</span>。（可叠加，最多叠加到3点）</p><p></p><p><strong><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">炽火大铠<br></span></strong><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 215, 128)\">出战状态</span></p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">我方角色普通攻击后：</span>造成1点<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 153, 153)\">火元素伤害</span>，生成<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">烈烧佑命护盾</span>。<br><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">可用次数：2</span></p>",
